      "code": "self.self.updateAttackStats({ air_ease: -1, canFallOff: false });\nself.self.attachEffect(\"global_dust_heavy\");\nSSF2API.getCamera().shake(3);\nif (self.self.getMetalStatus()) {\n\tself.self.playSound(\"metal_land_m\");\n\treturn;\n}\nself.self.playSound(\"falcon_dspecLand\");",
